<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      /* Email styles need to be inline */
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% images = ["https://theteenmagazine.s3.amazonaws.com/giphy.gif", "http://s3.amazonaws.com/theteenmagazine/Users/miajohansson/Desktop/ttm/blog/public/ckeditor_assets/pictures/2/content_3ZJ5ZIO.gif", "http://s3.amazonaws.com/theteenmagazine/Users/miajohansson/Desktop/ttm/blog/public/ckeditor_assets/pictures/1/content_giphy-1.gif"] %>
    <p>Hi <%= @pitch.title %>,</p>
    <p>Your interview <%= link_to @post.title, @post, style: "color: #4ABEB6;" %> was just published!</p>
    <% if @pitch.platform_to_share.present? && (!@pitch.platform_to_share.eql? "None selected") %>
      <p>
        To support our teenage writers, we kindly ask that you share the article using 
        <%= indefinite_articlerize(@pitch.platform_to_share) %> <b><%= @pitch.platform_to_share&.chomp(' (preferred)')&.sub('w/', 'with') %></b>.
        Please reply to this email once you have done so. If you are no longer able to share the link like you indicated in your interview request 
        or prefer to use a different platform, please inform us via email.
      </p>
    <% end %>
    <p>
      We greatly appreciate interviewing, and featuring, you on The Teen Magazine!
      <% if !@pitch.platform_to_share.present? || (@pitch.platform_to_share.eql? "None selected") %>
        If you are happy with how the interview turned out, please consider sharing the link on social media to support our teenage writers.
      <% end %>
      If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to send us an email. Congratulations!
    </p>
    <p>Best Regards,<br/>
      Mia Johansson</p>
  </body>
</html>
